title: Ubehage's EasyCopy v2 (Beta 2, v0.2.2)
description:
Ubehage's EasyCopy v2 (Beta 2, v0.2.2)
--------------------------------------

Here is the second Beta-release.

A few bugs has been fixed:
- Attributes were not preserved on files or folders.
- "Division by Zero" in Copy-module.
- If a file had a length of zero bytes, the Copy-module would crash.
- "Shutdown when finished" has been fixed.


For all of you who has no idea what this is, here is some screenshots: 
http://i.imgur.com/o0uLhss.jpg 
http://i.imgur.com/0oZkMjR.jpg



/Ubehage
